# ============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS - ProductifyAI
# ============================================================================
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic PR review assignments.
# When a PR is opened that modifies files matching these patterns, the
# specified owners will automatically be requested for review.
#
# Syntax:
# -------
# pattern  @username @team
#
# Patterns:
# ---------
# * = all files
# *.js = all JS files
# /docs/ = docs directory
# /docs/* = files in docs (not subdirectories)
# /docs/** = docs and all subdirectories
#
# Multiple Owners:
# ----------------
# /src/  @owner1 @owner2
# At least one owner must approve
#
# Documentation:
# --------------
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# ============================================================================

# Default owners for everything (fallback)
