# ============================================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================================
#
# - CODEOWNERS must be in the repository's root, docs/, or .github/ directory
# - Patterns are matched from bottom to top (last match wins)
# - Branch protection rules can require CODEOWNER approval
# - Teams must have write access to be added as code owners
#
# To enable CODEOWNER approval requirement:
# 1. Go to: Settings → Branches → Branch protection rules
# 2. Add rule for 'main' or 'replit-agent'
# 3. Enable "Require review from Code Owners"
#
# ============================================================================

